{"tid":1298043,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街！玩膠玩出火","createTime":"2019-07-08T18:04:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T18:12:23.000Z","uid":111454,"like":8,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"370f232f0fb4e4866670fdff699e9b691d2e23f0","tid":1298043,"uid":111454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:04:26.000Z","msg":"首先先向咁多位出咗去嘅義士講聲唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事態來得太突然<br />\n<br />\n我相信 連登仔冇諗過會玩到咁大<br />\n同時我亦都相信班撚屌一毛唔會咁撚醒<br />\n識得玩膠分化<br />\n我亦都希望香港兒女識得分辨事實<br />\n唔會咁輕易畀人分化<br />\n我哋大家都係香港人<br />\n<br />\n我知，今次好戇鳩<br />\n但你有幾耐冇試過咁撚戇鳩<br />\n喺我眼中，我哋就好似好耐冇玩過膠咁<br />\n喺呢個艱辛而悲痛嘅抗爭中<br />\n係咪好耐冇試過有咁大粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老實講，我今晚好開心<br />\n好耐冇試過笑得咁盡興<br />\n望住連登嘅一個個假膠post<br />\n初時我都嚇親： 我屌！今晚有活動咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但諗深一層<br />\n望住一堆鬼畫符，又話金鐘好多人<br />\n我就知道，係膠<br />\n係源源不絕嘅膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我笑咗<br />\n因為真係好耐好耐冇試過咁膠<br />\n屌！ 點解呀！<br />\n唔應該咁樣㗎，<br />\n唔應該冇試過咁耐冇膠架<br />\n但係<br />\n我真係好耐好耐冇試過笑得咁開心<br />\n我諗，我哋只係好耐冇笑過<br />\n<br />\n對唔住，義士們<br />\n加油，香港人<br />\n不要沉溺在悲痛之中<br />\n不要被滿腔熱血所蒙蔽<br />\n保持腦袋<br />\n多與朋友聚聚<br />\n吸點迷因或貓咪<br />\n記住，我們一個都不能少<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dJJJGaB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdJJJGaB.jpg&h=f5681133&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c45000d27ebba5cc1608c33272a86ae9d46b55bc","tid":1298043,"uid":111454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:06:09.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f622263a1ad7bdbffcc998b3a9d10aae35a25b6a","tid":1298043,"uid":111454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:06:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"516f35cd9d5f024ff8d3ed41ecdc63cfb60a0a17","tid":1298043,"uid":111454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:06:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e02f7eaaf500fcf30a9c197667f70f7ee62df7c","tid":1298043,"uid":111454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:07:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22c04fded2e671e8b5e2a39b0de7cb748d782477","tid":1298043,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:07:34.000Z","msg":"放低堆link方便大家唔洗逐隻垃圾搵黎block<br />\n<br />\n膠post 道歉聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1297586\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1297586</a><br />\n<br />\n突發金鐘要人！金鐘要人！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1297071\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1297071</a><br />\n<br />\n「清袋行動」已經有共識！11.30開始行動！今次一舖清佢袋<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1297253\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1297253</a><br />\n<br />\n2330做野 醒目 現場開始多人 提防狗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1297018\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1297018</a><br />\n<br />\n仲加咩密 出去救人呀！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1297140\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1297140</a>"},{"pid":"7cf0fde40734345b4f58d0a1be8547e59f5ed0c1","tid":1298043,"uid":23222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:08:17.000Z","msg":"今日發夢因為金鐘要人而出咗黎嘅入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1297745\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1297745</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a4555887b6c91b3565b0fd50fe11eca4bc0d409f","tid":1298043,"uid":204459,"like":2,"disl